{
  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed development would be unacceptable in principle as it would prejudice the delivery of an allocated site. It would fail to apply a design-led approach that optimises the capacity of sites, including site allocations and would fail to create successful sustainable mixed-use places that make the best use of land. The proposal is therefore contrary to London Plan Policies GG2 and D3, Local Plan Policies IMP1, IMP2 and the intentions of the NPPF.",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed development, by reason of its inappropriate height, massing, and scale would fail to respond to the character and context of the surrounding area. The proposal would be contrary to London Plan Policies D4 and D6, and Local Plan Policies CC1, CC2 and SC4.",
    "Reason : 3 - The submitted energy statement fails to demonstrate that the development would maximise energy savings at each step of the energy hierarchy. It is therefore contrary to Local Plan Policies EQ1 and EQ2 and London Plan Policies SI2."
  ],
